37:04.657 --> 37:08.095
♪ I was a stick of dynamite
and it just was... ♪

37:08.138 --> 37:08.965
Hey!

37:11.229 --> 37:12.882
I love you.

37:12.926 --> 37:15.450
♪ All day, all night
Now I can't hide ♪

37:15.494 --> 37:17.017
I love you more.

37:17.060 --> 37:21.413
♪ Said I knew myself
but I guess I lied ♪

37:21.456 --> 37:24.807
♪ It's okay, it's okay
