♪ And it's all right

38:01.322 --> 38:02.758
CAPTAIN [over PA]:
Ladies and gentlemen,

38:02.802 --> 38:04.238
greetings, this is
your captain speaking.

38:04.282 --> 38:05.500
We're just about ready
to depart.

38:05.544 --> 38:07.633
We should be
right on schedule.

38:07.676 --> 38:09.765
I'd like to take
this time to thank you
for choosing our airline.

38:23.692 --> 38:27.348
Oh, my God, it's you!

38:27.392 --> 38:29.655
-She's precious!
-Mm-hmm.

38:32.962 --> 38:35.225
-It's you!
-It is.

38:44.322 --> 38:46.889
MARIANA:
I wanted you to have
the Mariana doll,

38:46.933 --> 38:48.891
and I'm keeping
the Callie doll.

38:48.935 --> 38:51.111
This way, we both have
a piece of each other.

38:56.159 --> 38:59.424
♪

39:09.564 --> 39:10.609
FLIGHT ATTENDANT:
Welcome aboard.

39:17.442 --> 39:20.358
["Bottle" by Broken Anchor
& Brad Gordon playing]

39:20.401 --> 39:21.228
Um...

39:22.447 --> 39:24.362
what are
you doing here?

39:25.885 --> 39:28.409
I-- I got a job in D.C.
I start in a week.

39:28.453 --> 39:30.368
What are
you doing here?

39:30.411 --> 39:33.240
Uh, same,
but I start tomorrow.

39:35.329 --> 39:39.115
Did Jude tell Carter
that I was going to D.C.?

39:39.159 --> 39:42.205
Uh, if he did,
Carter didn't tell me.

39:42.249 --> 39:43.772
I'm many things, Callie,

39:43.816 --> 39:45.426
but I'm not
a crazy stalker person.

39:45.470 --> 39:47.036
♪ Heart is drummin'

39:47.080 --> 39:49.996
♪ And life keeps comin'
like 1-2-3 ♪

39:50.039 --> 39:53.434
I guess the universe
has conspired again.

39:55.741 --> 39:58.091
Huh. Is this seat taken?

40:00.615 --> 40:01.660
No. It isn't.

40:03.270 --> 40:05.620
♪

40:10.799 --> 40:13.628
♪ Hello, hello again

40:13.672 --> 40:16.326
